#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Dictionary"
msgstr "i "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten;'s most basic mode is as a dictionary for looking up both English and "
"Japanese words. You can also add other dictionaries to &kiten;'s list."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; ' S Shingiro Ubwoko ni Nka A Inkoranyamagambo ya:  Hejuru Byombi na "
"Amagambo . &Ongera Ikindi Inkoranyamagambo Kuri &kiten; ' S Urutonde . "

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. You "
"can find more information at <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict."
"html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/"
"wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; na Nka i Mburabuzi Inkoranyamagambo . Gushaka Birenzeho Ibisobanuro: "
"Ku <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/edict.html\"> i Urubuga "
"&Ipaji </ulink> na <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic."
"html\"> i Urubuga &Ipaji </ulink> . "

